msg.msgText: The {0} level was changed, but the MQ Connectivity server could not be notified of the change.

msgExplanation.p: The MQ Connectivity server will continue to report log events at the previous level until it is restarted.

msgUserResponse.p: If the MQ Connectivity server log events are not at the desired level, restart the MQ Connectivity server or try setting the log level again.
